{"tid":1570561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"樂華邨休班警投訴2A巴士車長阻差辦公","createTime":"2019-09-15T06:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T16:06:34.000Z","uid":213167,"like":9,"dislike":105,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"24097e93cce524dfe75f3b83c48cc4e81b8d3c6f","tid":1570561,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"15/9【#警察濫捕】昨日下午有兩名持槍「#休班警」潛伏於 2A 巴士上，當巴士抵達牛頭角樂華邨巴士總站後，便向兩名手無寸鐵的青年人進行搜查及拘捕。期間，有人離開巴士車廂時失足，跌倒在巴士總站行人路上（俗稱「仆街」），及後更衊指青年人襲警，引來街坊指罵。<br />\n<br />\n而「休班警」處理拘捕行動時阻礙巴士站交通，令要開出的巴士班次取消。有受影響車長上前向「休班警」查詢警員編號，以繕寫失班報告時，反被「休班警」指阻差辦公，並指會向巴士公司作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n車長向本台指，事後得悉有人以非正式途徑向載通國際行政總監，前警務處助理處長許鎮德先生，就車長「阻礙警務人員執行職務」作出投訴，並要求巴士公司「秉公處理」及交代。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70822440_2418937551477265_199861552885530624_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQndL3kIEMjT8JwlDaPb1AsAvYl7OIyUJkl2e9M5w1lBPMazOEZM4-KGfTqFXOs0Pik&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&amp;oh=d7a69248723139dec0c500c8745b8b82&amp;oe=5E0BE462\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70822440_2418937551477265_199861552885530624_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQndL3kIEMjT8JwlDaPb1AsAvYl7OIyUJkl2e9M5w1lBPMazOEZM4-KGfTqFXOs0Pik%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.xx%26oh%3Dd7a69248723139dec0c500c8745b8b82%26oe%3D5E0BE462&h=8036bfe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a18cdc62d9518a00e1c432b191ccb78f60e7c82f","tid":1570561,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=12f0a883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"